### Simular Webhook de Mercado Pago
POST {{host}}/api/webhook/mercadopago
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: DonataDelDesierto

{
    "id": "123456788",
    "status": "approved",
    "amount": 1500.00,
    "description": "Pinta Donata del Desierto"
}

